201d I said yes. The Prophet repeated this three times,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25204,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/09\/11\/yahya-akhirah-acquire-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":33141,"position":4},"title":"Yahya on Akhirah: Seek Hereafter only, you will get the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Jawzi reported: Yahya ibn Mu\u2019adh, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cO son of Adam, you seek the world as one seeks what he must have, and you seek the Hereafter as one who has no need of it. The world will suffice you as long as you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/ibn-masud-zuhd-mustarih-mustarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33141,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Hereafter: One is either relieved or relieved from","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Wa\u2019il reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever acts to show off, Allah will show him off. Whoever acts to be heard, Allah will make him heard. Whoever lengthens himself to aggrandize himself, Allah will debase him. Whoever humbles himself reverently, Allah will raise him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_co